long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
🚀 Jump, Fly, Flip, and Dash! 🎵

Geometry Dash is now available as a Chrome extension, bringing the thrill of rhythm-based platforming right to your browser! Challenge your reflexes in this fast-paced game where every jump, flip, and dash matters. Navigate through treacherous obstacles, time your moves perfectly, and enjoy the adrenaline-pumping action.

Why Install the Geometry Dash Chrome Extension?
🎮 Instant Access – Play Geometry Dash anytime directly from your Chrome browser with no need to download or install large files!
🎶 Rhythm-Based Fun – Sync your movements with the catchy in-game music, and feel the pulse of each level as you dodge obstacles.
⚡ Fast-Paced Action – Reflexes are key! Jump over spikes, dodge barriers, and time your movements for maximum effect.
📈 Unlock Levels and Skins – Customize your character, unlock new skins, and conquer levels as you progress.
🕹️ One-Touch Controls – Simple controls, but endless challenges! With just one tap or click, you’ll be hooked!
🎯 Challenging Levels – Master challenging levels designed to test your patience, reflexes, and skill.
🔥 No Downloads – Play instantly from your browser without any extra downloads or installations.

Features:
Seamless Gameplay: Experience smooth performance directly in your browser, with no lag or interruptions.
Compete with Friends: Share your high scores and challenge your friends to beat your record!
Addictive Fun: Keep coming back to try and beat your previous score! The fun never stops in Geometry Dash.
Ready for the challenge? 🚀 Install the Geometry Dash Chrome Extension now and dive into an electrifying world of action, rhythm, and endless fun. Start dashing and test your reflexes to the max! 🎮💥
